Settings Manager--> Window Manager--> Keyboard--> Tile Windows... 

<Control><Left>
  Tile Left
<Control><Right>
  Tile Right
<Control><Up>
  Tile Up
<Control><Down>
  Tile Down

Settings Manager--> Window Manager--> Keyboard--> Maximize
<Control><Shift><Up>
  Maximize Window

Settings Manager--> Window Manager--> Keyboard--> Lower
<Control><Shift><Down>
  Lower Window
  
Settings Manager--> Keyboard--> Application Shortcuts...
<Control><Shift><Left>
  xdotool getactivewindow windowmove 0 77 windowsize 1920 1029
  (Move window full screen left monitor)
  
<Control><Shift><Right>
  xdotool getactivewindow windowmove 1920 52 windowsize 1280 998
  (Move window full screen right monitor)
  
Settings Manager--> Window Manager--> Keyboard--> Close
<Control><End>
  Close Window
  
Settings Manager--> Keyboard--> Application Shortcuts...
<Control><Shift><Escape>
  X-Kill
